線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"8333043bdf2689fdfa637b078081a6e5bf991940","tid":913691,"uid":16065,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T21:00:28.000Z","msg":"趾毛同指模差唔多用途，有人unlock手機嗰時唔想用指模認證就會用趾毛認證"},{"pid":"a6a34e61f5504aebff706c9f57ace80d09c44939","tid":913691,"uid":45920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T00:21:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">千</span></span>"},{"pid":"a9a8788fa6b3cd78f14bad26989701280ee2d565","tid":913691,"uid":105614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8333043bdf2689fdfa637b078081a6e5bf991940","tid":913691,"uid":16065,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T21:00:28.000Z","msg":"趾毛同指模差唔多用途，有人unlock手機嗰時唔想用指模認證就會用趾毛認證"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T00:57:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67051e82b6edf15e907ac989a6d7c75385f61d92","tid":913691,"uid":59920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a6a34e61f5504aebff706c9f57ace80d09c44939","tid":913691,"uid":45920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T00:21:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">千</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T01:05:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">奇</span></span>"},{"pid":"b6885a1adbe3b009a052ac88d916b33bb3d2acb3","tid":913691,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T01:49:19.000Z","msg":"有蟲仔爬過會FEEL到, 有毛敏感D"},{"pid":"c3d48e9ae3bed006fde9f98927a9755544d755bc","tid":913691,"uid":130901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8333043bdf2689fdfa637b078081a6e5bf991940","tid":913691,"uid":16065,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T21:00:28.000Z","msg":"趾毛同指模差唔多用途，有人unlock手機嗰時唔